{"tid":1390425,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"望遠啲，罷工都要升級","createTime":"2019-07-31T06:44:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-31T07:17:38.000Z","uid":27718,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"8298c373d0104ab431eb26c8f7b82183ca0d4da2","tid":1390425,"uid":27718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T06:44:15.000Z","msg":"<strong><ins>罷工第一次</ins></strong><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />首先有一堆人唔會罷<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />啲腦細當放一日假<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />個政府采鳩你都傻，當打風<br />\n<br />\n1969 年，正值美國反越戰運動高峰期，活躍社運的反戰僱主 Jerome Grossman 提出，要發動全國大罷市反對越戰，策略是<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">每個月罷市一日</span></span></strong>，若然政府一個月內未有讓步，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>下個月則罷市兩日</strong></span></span>，如此類推，罷市日數不斷遞增。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>罷工第二次</ins></strong>，要罷兩日<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />同樣會有一堆人唔會罷，但佢會開始覺得自己好on9<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />腦細開始有壓力<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />個政府開始淆底<br />\n<br />\n罷工第三次，要罷三日<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />自己諗<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔可以再停留喺覺得罷工一日就有用<br />\n正如<br />\n你每年七一遊行一日唔會有用<br />\n變成每個月遊行一日都係冇用<br />\n你要每星期甚至日撚日都遊行先會有啲用"},{"pid":"9deb8eb833d4230db2f10df5a8a0c0497a2d5556","tid":1390425,"uid":27718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T06:52:15.000Z","msg":"罷一日無撚用"},{"pid":"8d8209297ba4b116de7da207bf3aa97fd832e4cc","tid":1390425,"uid":27718,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T06:52:32.000Z","msg":"每個月罷先有用"},{"pid":"ebfd5aedee1d7ea7dac814b137e60edb5d36b164","tid":1390425,"uid":27718,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T06:52:46.000Z","msg":"1969 年，正值美國反越戰運動高峰期，活躍社運的反戰僱主 Jerome Grossman 提出，要發動全國大罷市反對越戰，策略是每個月罷市一日，若然政府一個月內未有讓步，下個月則罷市兩日，如此類推，罷市日數不斷遞增。<br />\n<br />\n罷工都要逐步升級<br />\n<br />\n八月罷工一日<br />\n九月罷工兩日<br />\n十月罷工三日<br />\n十一月罷工四日<br />\n十二月罷工五日<br />\n<br />\n如果無人理我地<br />\n一兩年後香港人就唔洗返工喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b38e3c8be2abc1f1234ce0b5df4c62e7d0f3638f","tid":1390425,"uid":16007,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T06:53:52.000Z","msg":"今次罷一日係開一個先例<br />\n我覺得而家能夠做到一日已經好難得"},{"pid":"337f57abfd1feceadfc4ffe4f62eda93e127fe86","tid":1390425,"uid":226955,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T06:54:28.000Z","msg":"不要說「推」，試着説「8月5號齊罷工」<br />\n<br />\n範例：<br />\n<blockquote>#我係香港人 <br />\n#我會參與8月5日三罷 <br />\n#罷工罷市罷課</blockquote>"},{"pid":"8d02849ef946cca6d5b1849f9acecdbbb7a3dbe8","tid":1390425,"uid":262022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T06:55:05.000Z","msg":"8月5號齊罷工"},{"pid":"12329513233f74a2acdb91374ec6077303676969","tid":1390425,"uid":181088,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T07:00:38.000Z","msg":"做左第一日先講啦⋯⋯<br />\n最撚驚我地吹咁大<br />\n最後冇件咁事⋯"},{"pid":"565b66c81e4984f9ab83d7f814d68aad59d3461a","tid":1390425,"uid":262342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T07:17:38.000Z","msg":"#我係香港人 <br />\n#我會參與8月5日三罷 <br />\n#罷工罷市罷課"}]}